text: average sized to hold a decent crowd size at times. also offers up a decent shade from the sun.

There is North Point mall, a movie theatre, bus terminal, hdb eateries and shops, community clubs , a polyclinic all within walking distance. Further down there is Khoo Teck Phuat hospital and Safra club.  It is great place to hang out if there is no covid. The only negative comment is that it can get quite crowded at peak hours and affect shopping experience.
Bus 103 is always late. From 2 mins to 3, then to 4 mins... till the next bus comes
